53399b9f-391e-421f-b472-f19b81d5edba.title: <player>
53399b9f-391e-421f-b472-f19b81d5edba.text: Hi, I've just spoken with Bonafido. Interesting chap.

1385fca8-b76a-44ab-9d6e-435a9f0f8696.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
1385fca8-b76a-44ab-9d6e-435a9f0f8696.text:
Yes, if by interesting you mean lazy, slow and
worthless.

029706fe-cd49-4fad-93d5-cf5cb7610b71.title: <player>
029706fe-cd49-4fad-93d5-cf5cb7610b71.text: My skills tell me you're not the best of friends.

b29d0339-9b75-49be-978e-c0a99e7f2b15.title: <player>
b29d0339-9b75-49be-978e-c0a99e7f2b15.text: I've agreed to help you with this tower; what's it for?

8c02f036-cdc4-4b5f-85f1-62b27b7dc1b0.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
8c02f036-cdc4-4b5f-85f1-62b27b7dc1b0.text: Then I'm afraid I can't say.

bf373365-708c-4dbc-a247-09ecfd5a1daa.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
bf373365-708c-4dbc-a247-09ecfd5a1daa.text: Hey, while you're there, could you lend us a few coins?

83bd7994-4b9d-42fe-b06d-b7c8dfee41fc.title: <player>
83bd7994-4b9d-42fe-b06d-b7c8dfee41fc.text:
You're obsessed with money. What do you think I am:
a bank?

6e8c1e75-5fac-4a31-9a25-c0a42bb0965f.title: <player>
6e8c1e75-5fac-4a31-9a25-c0a42bb0965f.text: Hi. Sorry, but why do they call you 'Currency'?

7a931ec6-b9fe-4d8b-ac6f-15c3957fea33.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
7a931ec6-b9fe-4d8b-ac6f-15c3957fea33.text:
That's down to my interest in all things of monetary
value.

d2fead0a-21e5-4b48-9bb5-61f9d9946951.title: <player>
d2fead0a-21e5-4b48-9bb5-61f9d9946951.text: You must be pretty rich then.

62f6af06-b303-4b6c-8c8b-209e468c5722.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
62f6af06-b303-4b6c-8c8b-209e468c5722.text: I wish. And I was, up until recently.

f4b2b090-5433-4b7a-b834-f0cd09134548.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
f4b2b090-5433-4b7a-b834-f0cd09134548.text: This tower. Set me back a fair few million.

9f6963ac-bdc8-49c2-a24a-552f8c6cb1ef.title: <player>
9f6963ac-bdc8-49c2-a24a-552f8c6cb1ef.text:
I'll bet! It pleases you, then, to know that I have just
become a builder and have been granted permission to
go mess around inside.

44023d65-22d9-4a1d-bf52-50e8a3b51627.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
44023d65-22d9-4a1d-bf52-50e8a3b51627.text: This is not a good day for me.

959ff7e7-ea8e-4d5c-abaf-2dbbb44c916f.title: <player>
959ff7e7-ea8e-4d5c-abaf-2dbbb44c916f.text: Hi, Currency. Got any spare cash?

a7c59565-c15c-4cb9-af3f-ee4b5571121b.title: <player>
a7c59565-c15c-4cb9-af3f-ee4b5571121b.text: I'm going to stop before this gets violent.

dd1a38bc-b479-4444-a97a-99e32f5a7ae4.title: <player>
dd1a38bc-b479-4444-a97a-99e32f5a7ae4.text: That is one very sad creature.

68d51457-d790-4275-9f18-97edc6c1745a.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
68d51457-d790-4275-9f18-97edc6c1745a.text: It'll be alright; it just needs a pat on the back.

affce886-58c5-4fcf-8fd1-f4c27de00013.title: <player>
affce886-58c5-4fcf-8fd1-f4c27de00013.text:
Why am I suddenly glad that you're not responsible
for sorting out this mess?

bf4e0350-edfd-4aaa-bcf9-1f1ea8409568.title: <player>
bf4e0350-edfd-4aaa-bcf9-1f1ea8409568.text: Okay, I'm going to go chat with the Homunculus.

12613e0d-0e1c-45c9-9b7b-3c3fe6818dd8.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
12613e0d-0e1c-45c9-9b7b-3c3fe6818dd8.text: Could you do us a favour?

affb8840-2342-44c9-b7fd-1a1146763c62.title: <player>
affb8840-2342-44c9-b7fd-1a1146763c62.text:
I probably have enough on my plate, but go ahead;
what?

e1ca5698-089f-4837-9a5f-5f3e6457e754.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
e1ca5698-089f-4837-9a5f-5f3e6457e754.text: Could you ask it a question?

5d80c2dc-2e49-4de9-8699-69dcfc18fbad.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
5d80c2dc-2e49-4de9-8699-69dcfc18fbad.text: Does it have any spare cash?

4b8f0be3-2f2e-47e1-ab1d-3115196fdfa2.title: <player>
4b8f0be3-2f2e-47e1-ab1d-3115196fdfa2.text: Let me think how I can phrase this...

5cf1275b-ff04-4b93-b36b-1f04209649c5.title: <player>
5cf1275b-ff04-4b93-b36b-1f04209649c5.text: The Homunculus is a bit better off now.

08ed2def-3aef-4bc2-bdd6-10a3ee88c58f.title: 'Currency' The Alchemist
08ed2def-3aef-4bc2-bdd6-10a3ee88c58f.text: Excellent. So we can go back in.
